This plugin allows to extend Your theme functionality with XML Components.
You can create, modify custom XML files inside admin panel and get access to it through one simple function &quot;return&amp;#95;xml&amp;#95;component&quot;.
Plugin contains very usable ACE Editor for XML.

**USAGE:**

1. Install plugin; 
2. Log in into admin panel and push tab &quot;XML Components&quot;; 
3. Create or modify Your XML component (which is simple XML file); 
4. Push &quot;Save&quot; button; 
5. Use it in Your template via **return&amp;#95;xml&amp;#95;component(&amp;lt;name&amp;gt;)** function. This *function returns simple string*, not XML object, thus You could use any xml engine You like.

